ed="T" n="0727c19"/><persName key="A001582">釋靖邁</persName>，<placeName key="PL000000035550">梓潼</placeName>人也。少孺矜持，長高志操，特<lb
ed="T" n="0727c20"/>於經論研覈造微<ptr type="glossary" target="#g557"/>。氣性沈厚，不妄交結，遊<lb
ed="T" n="0727c21"/>必擇方，抵于<ref type="place" target="#PL000000042189">京輔</ref>。<date notBefore-iso="+0627-01-26" key="j19500921958507" notAfter-iso="+0650-02-09">貞觀中</date>，屬<persName key="A000294">玄奘</persName>西迴，勅<lb
ed="T" n="0727c22"/>奉為<persName key="A006400">太穆太后</persName>於<placeName key="PL000000042189">京</placeName>造<placeName key="PL000000042305">廣福寺</placeName>，就彼翻譯。<lb
ed="T" n="0727c23"/>所須吏力，悉與<persName key="A002115">玄齡</persName>商量，務令優給。遂召<lb
ed="T" n="0727c24"/>證義<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g54"/>大德諳練大小乘經論，為時所尊尚<lb
ed="T" n="0727c25"/>者，得一十一人，<persName key="A001582">邁</persName>預其精選，即居<placeName key="PL000000042410">慈恩寺</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0727c26"/>也。同<placeName key="PL000000042290">普光寺</placeName><persName key="A009208">棲玄</persName>、<placeName key="PL000000042305">廣福寺</placeName><persName key="A009209">明濬</persName>、<placeName key="PL000000042338">會昌寺</placeName><persName key="A001966">辯機</persName>、<lb
ed="T" n="0727c27"/><placeName key="PL000000042505">終南山豐德寺</placeName><persName key="A001519">道宣</persName>同執筆綴文，翻譯《本<lb
ed="T" n="0727c28"/>事經》七卷。<persName key="A001582">邁</persName>後與<persName key="A009198">神昉</persName>筆受<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g53"/>於<placeName key="PL000000042745">玉華宮</placeName>及<placeName key="PL000000042411">慈<lb
ed="T" n="0727c29"/>恩寺翻經院</placeName>，皆推適變，故得經心矣。後著<pb ed="T" n="0728a" xml:id="T50.2061.0728a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0728a01"/>《譯經圖紀》四卷，銓序古今經目、譯人名位、單<lb
ed="T" n="0728a02"/>譯、重翻、疑偽等科，一皆條理，見編于《藏》。<date notBefore-iso="+0713-12-26" key="j19818371992113" notAfter-iso="+0742-02-13">開元<lb
ed="T" n="0728a03"/>中</date>，<persName key="A001261">智昇</persName>又續其題目<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1243"/>焉。</p>
